.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, black, azure, coral
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, librarian, pilot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the pilot##8
 2. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person who likes coral is the freelancer##1
 5. the electrician is not the person who likes azure##6
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the person who likes coral is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | azure          | ivory      | coral      | black   |
| Job        | librarian     | electrician | freelancer | pilot      |
| Sport      | weightlifting | baseball    | badminton  | ice-hockey |

