.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, reading, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b, techno
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros, bongani, pall-mall
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 5. the game-smoker is not the fan of blues##6
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 7. the fan of blues is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading  | filmmaking | sudoku | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | country  | blues      | techno | d&b        |
| Cigar     | game | bongani       | pall-mall    | oliveros     |

