.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, horror, mystery, thriller
There 4 different types of food: onion, cranberry, apple, cucumber
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, german, thai
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 2. the colombian is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
 3. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the colombian##8
 6. the german is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 7. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 8. the thai is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
 9. the chinese is on the left of the german##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is the german##1
11. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | thriller | horror    | mystery |
| Food   | apple    | cranberry     | onion   | cucumber     |
| Nationality   | chinese | german   | colombian | thai    |

