 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the train is not the palace house##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the palace house##8
 9. the palace house is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
10. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the palace house##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
