The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
2. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the owner of the chinchilla##7
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
7. the owner of the snake is the fan of jazz##1
8. the owner of the snake is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person drinking fanta##7
9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | coffee | iced-tea  | soy-milk |
| Pet          | cat | snake   | horse | chinchilla |
| Music-Genre   | house     | jazz   | rock      | pop      |

