4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person drinking water is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is handball##7
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking mirinda##1

